What is one-to-one association between classes?
An entity object is associated with only one entity object of another class then it is said to be in one-to-one association with each other.
  (or)

In a class if we hold only one object of another class and even viceversa then the entities are said to be in one-to-one association with each other.
  
How to model an entity classes with one-to-one association into database tables?
There are 2 ways are there
  1. direct one-to-one
  2. one-to-many as one-to-one

